<content>
    <chapter line="1">12. Vacchagottasaṃyuttavaṇṇanā</chapter>
    <paragraph line="2" number="607-661"><bold>Aññāṇā</bold>ti <pageBreak edition="Vipassana Research Institut" number="2.0253" /> aññāṇahetu, saccapaṭicchādakasammohahetūti attho. Aṭṭhakathāyaṃ pana imameva atthaṃ hetuatthena karaṇavacanena dassetuṃ <bold>‘‘aññāṇenā’’</bold>ti vuttaṃ. <bold>Sabbānī</bold>ti ‘‘aññāṇā adassanā anabhisamayā’’tiādīni padāni ekādasasu suttesu āgatāni, pañcapaññāsa veyyākaraṇāni vuttāni suttesu pañcannaṃ khandhānaṃ vasena veyyākaraṇassa āgatattā.</paragraph>
    <centered line="3">Vacchagottasaṃyuttavaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā.</centered>
  </content>
